Package me.hapyl.spigotutils.module.player.tablist

Class Tablist

java.lang.Object
me.hapyl.spigotutils.module.player.tablist.Tablist
public class Tablist extends Object
A four column customizable tab list.
Keep in mind this relies on player's scoreboard! Changing it with Player.setScoreboard(Scoreboard) will break the tablist!
